          <strong>Important:</strong> Installing BrewOS involves working with electrical systems 
          that can be dangerous. You assume all risks associated with installing, modifying, or 
          using BrewOS on your espresso machine.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Always disconnect power before working on your machine</li>
          <li>Ensure proper grounding and electrical safety</li>
          <li>Follow your machine manufacturer's guidelines</li>
          <li>Consult a qualified electrician if unsure</li>
